{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The backend surfaced a real bug during restore: restoring a prior accepted segment tried to write a second story asset to the exact same object path as the accepted rewrite snapshot. I\u2019m fixing the asset snapshot naming so version select...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_158", "text": "The backend surfaced a real bug during restore: restoring a prior accepted segment tried to write a second story asset to the exact same object path as the accepted rewrite snapshot. I\u2019m fixing the asset snapshot naming so version selection produces a distinct durable artifact, then I\u2019ll rerun the touched backend and frontend suites.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 300, "prompt_index": 68, "prompt_name": "67 \u2014 Diff and Compare UI for Rewrites", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T12:38:24-07:00"}
