{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented and committed as `1e1d30c` (`feat(prompt-67): diff and compare ui`). The rewrite flow now has a reusable compare panel in composition and finalize, with highlighted segment diffs, accept/reject/try-another controls for pendin...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_277", "text": "Implemented and committed as `1e1d30c` (`feat(prompt-67): diff and compare ui`).\n\nThe rewrite flow now has a reusable compare panel in composition and finalize, with highlighted segment diffs, accept/reject/try-another controls for pending rewrites, and restore support for older accepted revisions. Backend support was added for rejecting rewrite jobs and selecting an active saved segment version, including canonical text snapshot updates and downstream stale-marking when a restored revision invalidates later text.\n\nVerification completed:\n- `pytest backend/tests/test_story_tools.py backend/tests/test_session_api.py` \u2014 73 passed\n- `ruff check app tests` \u2014 passed\n- `npm test -- --run src/features/session/segmentVersionDiff.test.ts src/features/session/CompositionStage.test.tsx src/features/session/FinalizeStage.test.tsx` \u2014 8 passed\n- `npm test -- --run src/pages/session/SessionWorkspacePage.test.tsx` \u2014 32 passed\n- `npm run lint` \u2014 passed\n- `npm run build` \u2014 passed\n- Live browser QA against the running Compose stack, with screenshots at:\n  - `/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/tools/webapp-qa/.artifacts/prompt-67/composition-pending-desktop.png`\n  - `/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/tools/webapp-qa/.artifacts/prompt-67/composition-pending-panel.png`\n  - `/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/tools/webapp-qa/.artifacts/prompt-67/composition-pending-mobile.png`\n  - `/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/tools/webapp-qa/.artifacts/prompt-67/finalize-restore-desktop.png`\n  - `/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/tools/webapp-qa/.artifacts/prompt-67/finalize-restore-panel.png`\n\nThe required reviewer summary was written last to [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/67_diff_and_compare_ui_for_rewrites/summary.md).", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 527, "prompt_index": 68, "prompt_name": "67 \u2014 Diff and Compare UI for Rewrites", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T12:56:27-07:00"}
